constraints. Whether the quotes or stories themselves are true seem to be
of secondary importance. In any event, we apologize not only to Tony but
to the Fijian Government for any embarrassments and for our amplifying an
erroneous story. It seems the dengue outbreak in Fiji is being handled
properly and with dispatch. - Mod.CHC
